==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Knee jerk reaction
<hw>Knee jerk reaction</hw>. <def>an immediate unthinking emotional
reaction produced by an event or statement to which the reacting person
is highly sensitive; -- in persons with strong feelings on a topic, it
may be very predictable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kneejoint</ent>⟦br⟧
